example/showcase/

# Keep only essential files for pub.dev:
# - lib/ (required)
# - README.md (required)
# - CHANGELOG.md (required)
# - LICENSE (required)
# - pubspec.yaml (required)
# - shaders/ (required)
# - example/lib/ (recommended)
# - example/pubspec.yaml (recommended)
# - test/ (optional but good practice)
